      "rationale": "RH index predictions compared against FDA bench measurements at five operating points. Normalized RMS error is 9.4%. Maximum pointwise error is 14.1% at the highest flow-speed combination. Errors are within the experimental measurement uncertainty band (±15%) at all points. Comparison deemed sufficient for MRL 2."
