      "rationale": "Use error assessment (e.g., formal FMEA of analyst workflow) is not mandated at MRL 2 with medium model influence. Standard operating procedures govern mesh generation, boundary condition assignment, and post-processing. Independent peer review of simulation setup was conducted. Factor recorded as not-assessed per MRL 2 sufficiency table."
